nse-and-re-open-if-it-can-meet-robust-safety-rules-3498784">只要满足 77 条“严格”安全规则，该场馆就可以保留其许可证并重新开放</a>。</p><p>完成后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-announces-reopening-details-with-first-gig-3596293">它将在下个月重新开放</a>，开幕表演包括 Nirvana UK（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬）、The Smyths（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">The Smiths</a>致敬）、Definitemightbe（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>致敬）和 UK Foo Fighters（向 The Smiths 致敬）和 UK Foo Fighters（向 The Smiths 致敬）<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">喷火战机</a>）。</p><p>除此之外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/editors">编辑们</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/editors-announce-huge-show-at-londons-re-opened-brixton-academy-buy-tickets-3596360">宣布将于 5 月 2 日星期四在伦敦标志性场地举办一场演出</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-BLACK-KEYS">The Black Keys</a>将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-announce-2024-uk-shows-including-brixton-academy-dates-buy-tickets-3596362">5 月 7 日星期二和 5 月 8 日星期三进行两晚的驻场演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bleachers-announce-2024-uk-and-european-shows-including-brixton-academy-gig-3601155">Bleachers 宣布 2024 年英国和欧洲演出（包括 Brixton Academy 演出）的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
